  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA42">
<l>tirumakaḷu maṇmakaḷu māymakaḷuñ cērntāṟ</l>
<l>ṟirumakaṭkē tīrntavā ṟeṉkol – tirumakaṇmēṟ</l>
<l>pālōtañ cintap paṭanā kaṇaikkiṭanta</l>
<l>mālōta vaṇṇar maṉam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the Lady Śrī, the earth lady and the cowherd lady join [him],</l>
<l>what is [this] way that it stops at the Lady Śrī,</l>
<l>the mind of him with the colour of the dark flood</l>
<l>who rested on the hooded-serpent bed while the milk flood is spilled on Śrī?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
